 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213213106/http://pdglive.lbl.gov/Rsummary.brl?nodein=Q007
 |dead-url     = yes
}}</ref>。和其他夸克一样，顶夸克属于[[费米子|费米子]]，具有{{frac|1|2}}的[[自旋|自旋]]，带有+{{frac|2|3}}电荷。<ref name="Willenbrock">{{cite book
